      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "欢迎来到圆锥曲线实验！今天我们要探索三种美丽的曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.41,
      "size": 38592,
      "text": "椭圆、双曲线和抛物线，它们有一个共同的名字：圆锥曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "为什么叫圆锥曲线？因为它们都可以通过切割圆锥得到。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "cone-cutting",
      "line_id": "cone-cutting-1",
      "filename": "cone-cutting-cone-cutting-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/cone-cutting-cone-cutting-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "想象一个双圆锥，就是两个圆锥顶点对顶点连在一起。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "cone-cutting",
      "line_id": "cone-cutting-2",
      "filename": "cone-cutting-cone-cutting-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/cone-cutting-cone-cutting-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "用一个平面去切割它，根据切割角度的不同，会得到不同的曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "cone-cutting",
      "line_id": "cone-cutting-3",
      "filename": "cone-cutting-cone-cutting-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/cone-cutting-cone-cutting-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.55,
      "size": 24768,
      "text": "水平切割得到圆，倾斜切割得到椭圆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "cone-cutting",
      "line_id": "cone-cutting-4",
      "filename": "cone-cutting-cone-cutting-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/cone-cutting-cone-cutting-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "平行于母线切割得到抛物线，更陡的角度切割得到双曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "ellipse",
      "line_id": "ellipse-1",
      "filename": "ellipse-ellipse-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/ellipse-ellipse-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "椭圆是到两个定点距离之和为常数的点的轨迹。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "ellipse",
      "line_id": "ellipse-2",
      "filename": "ellipse-ellipse-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/ellipse-ellipse-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "这两个定点叫做焦点，用F1和F2表示。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "ellipse",
      "line_id": "ellipse-3",
      "filename": "ellipse-ellipse-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/ellipse-ellipse-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.67,
      "size": 42768,
      "text": "椭圆的标准方程是x平方除以a平方加y平方除以b平方等于1。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "ellipse",
      "line_id": "ellipse-4",
      "filename": "ellipse-ellipse-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/ellipse-ellipse-4.mp3",
      "duration": 3.09,
      "size": 49392,
      "text": "其中a是长半轴，b是短半轴，焦距c满足c平方等于a平方减b平方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "ellipse-demo",
      "line_id": "ellipse-demo-1",
      "filename": "ellipse-demo-ellipse-demo-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/ellipse-demo-ellipse-demo-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.64,
      "size": 26208,
      "text": "图中显示的是一个椭圆，两个红点是焦点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "ellipse-demo",
      "line_id": "ellipse-demo-2",
      "filename": "ellipse-demo-ellipse-demo-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/ellipse-demo-ellipse-demo-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "拖动椭圆上的点，观察它到两个焦点的距离之和。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "ellipse-demo",
      "line_id": "ellipse-demo-3",
      "filename": "ellipse-demo-ellipse-demo-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/ellipse-demo-ellipse-demo-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "无论点在椭圆上的什么位置，这个距离之和始终不变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "ellipse-demo",
      "line_id": "ellipse-demo-4",
      "filename": "ellipse-demo-ellipse-demo-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/ellipse-demo-ellipse-demo-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.66,
      "size": 26496,
      "text": "调整参数a和b，观察椭圆形状的变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "hyperbola",
      "line_id": "hyperbola-1",
      "filename": "hyperbola-hyperbola-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/hyperbola-hyperbola-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "双曲线是到两个定点距离之差的绝对值为常数的点的轨迹。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "hyperbola",
      "line_id": "hyperbola-2",
      "filename": "hyperbola-hyperbola-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/hyperbola-hyperbola-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "注意是距离之差，而椭圆是距离之和。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "hyperbola",
      "line_id": "hyperbola-3",
      "filename": "hyperbola-hyperbola-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/hyperbola-hyperbola-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.6,
      "size": 25632,
      "text": "双曲线有两支，分别在两个焦点的两侧。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "hyperbola",
      "line_id": "hyperbola-4",
      "filename": "hyperbola-hyperbola-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/hyperbola-hyperbola-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "双曲线还有两条渐近线，曲线会无限接近但永远不会碰到它们。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "parabola",
      "line_id": "parabola-1",
      "filename": "parabola-parabola-1.mp3",
