      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "对于椭圆，e等于c除以a，取值在0到1之间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "eccentricity",
      "line_id": "eccentricity-3",
      "filename": "eccentricity-eccentricity-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/eccentricity-eccentricity-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "e越接近0，椭圆越接近圆；e越接近1，椭圆越扁。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "eccentricity",
      "line_id": "eccentricity-4",
      "filename": "eccentricity-eccentricity-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/conic-sections/yunxi/eccentricity-eccentricity-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "抛物线的离心率恰好等于1，双曲线的离心率大于1。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "conic-sections",
      "section_id": "applications",
